<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِجَهَالَةٍ}</span> ... بِسَفَهٍ، وَكُلُّ مَنْ عَصَى اللهَ فَهُوَ جَاهِلٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِن قَرِيبٍ}</span> ... قَبْلَ مُعَايَنَةِ المَوْتِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا تَعْضُلُوهُنَّ}</span> ... لَا تُمْسِكُوهُنَّ مُضَارِّينَ لَهُنَّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قِنطَارًا}</span> ... مَالًا كَثِيرًا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بُهْتَانًا}</span> ... كَذِبًا، وَظُلْمًا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَفْضَى}</span> ... اسْتَمْتَعَ بِالْجِمَاعِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَقْتًا}</span> ... بَغِيضًا يَمْقُتُ اللهُ فَاعِلَهُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَبِيلًا}</span> ... طَرِيقًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَرَبَائِبُكُمُ}</span> ... بَنَاتُ نِسَائِكُمُ اللَّاتِي يَتَرَبَّيْنَ غَالِبًا فِي بُيُوتِكُمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَحَلَائِلُ}</span> ... زَوْجَاتُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْمُحْصَنَاتُ}</span> ... المُتَزَوِّجَاتُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَا مَلَكَتْ أَيْمَانُكُمْ}</span> ... المَسْبِيَّاتُ، وَهُنَّ المَاخُوذَاتُ مِنْ نِسَاءِ الكُفَّارِ فِي الجِهَادِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
